Program â€“
prompt = "Please enter your age."
prompt += "\nEnter 'quit' when you are finished. "

while True:
    age = input(prompt)
    if age == 'quit':
        break
    age = int(age)
    if age < 3:
        print("  You get a free ticket for the movie!")
    elif age < 13:
        print("  Your ticket cost $10 for the movie.")
    else:
        print("  Your ticket cost $15 for the movie.")

Output - 
Please enter your age.
Enter 'quit' when you are finished. 6
  Your ticket cost $10 for the movie.
Please enter your age.
Enter 'quit' when you are finished. 2
  You get a free ticket for the movie!
Please enter your age.
Enter 'quit' when you are finished. 18
  Your ticket cost $15 for the movie.
Please enter your age.
Enter 'quit' when you are finished. quit
